desc:
Established in 2015, Dongyang Shenzhong supply chain Co., Ltd is a professional manufacturer specialized in design, development and production of fanny pack, compression socks, leggings, outdoor products, bikinis, etc. All of our products comply with international quality standards and are highly admired by a variety of markets throughout the world. We provide one-stop OEM and ODM solutions for clients.  For quick quotation within 24 hours and free samples, simply send enquiry to us.



---Our Motive---


When comfort becomes your motto
Your good looks are also an important part of well-being.
Our products are defined by soft, comfort and exceptional durability.

At the same time, they maintain the body's natural ability to regulate heat. Which means that they cool you during physical activity and provide warmth when temperatures drop down.

The garments ensure the satisfying experience, which is confirmed again and again by a large group of satisfied customers.

Our motive is to have better fibers and cloth that enable a better life.
